<p>If you are a California resident and would like to make such a request, please submit your request in writing to us using the contact information provided in Section 17. In your request, please attest that you are a California resident and provide a current California address for our response. We will respond to your request within 30 days.</p>

<!-- 15. NEVADA RESIDENTS -->
<h2>15. Nevada Residents</h2>
<p>Under Nevada Revised Statutes Chapter 603A (NRS 603A.345), Nevada residents have the right to submit a verified request directing us not to sell their "covered information" (as defined under Nevada law) that we have collected or will collect about them. A "sale" under Nevada law means the exchange of covered information for monetary consideration to a person for that person to license or sell the covered information to additional persons.</p>
<p>If you are a Nevada resident and wish to exercise your right to opt out of the sale of your covered information, please contact us using the information provided in Section 17. We will respond to your request within 60 days, or 90 days if we reasonably need additional time, in which case we will notify you of the delay and the reason for the extension.</p>

